last_episode_to_air.name: Ikusa Otome Suvia
last_episode_to_air.overview: The King of Hell has held Odin, the ruler of the Norse gods, captured in the Land of the Dead with the help of Loki, the Trickster. Valkyrie failed to save her and eventually became a sex slave to the devil. As an exchange to free herself, Odin had a river source to a sealed World Tree, which would destroy the whole world. But before that, Loki told Freya, Head of the Valkyrie, to be arrested to fight Odin's plan. To prevent the World of Trees from falling, Loki had to find 2 keys that were protected by 2 Valkyries namely invincible Sigurd & Suvia. And Loki turned his attention to Suvia the Princess of Prishintia.
